      • dumpBeanToString

        public static String dumpBeanToString(String qry)
                               throws MalformedObjectNameException,
                                      IOException
        Returns a subset of mbeans defined by qry. Modeled after DumpRegionServerMetrics#dumpMetrics. Example: String qry= "java.lang:type=Memory"
        返回:
        String representation of json array.
        抛出:
        MalformedObjectNameException - if json have bad format
        IOException - /
